  <brief_title>Database of Tissue Samples to Understand the Inflammatory Response After Cardiac Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Non-individual Related Ongoing Collection of Blood Samples for the Compilation of a Unique Database of Tissue Samples to Understand the Inflammatory Response After Cardiac Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
